articles.title: At least 61 dead, 45 rescued in huge fire at hypermarket in Iraq's Kut
articles.description: A fire at a mall in Iraq has resulted in at least 60 deaths, according to officials [2, 5].

articles.title: Voting age to be lowered for next election - and bank cards accepted as ID
articles.description: The UK is set to lower the voting age and accept bank cards as valid forms of identification for the next election [1, 4].

articles.title: 'Rain emergency' declared in Pakistan's Punjab after 30 dead in 24 hours
articles.description: Due to heavy monsoon rains, a rain emergency has been declared in Punjab, Pakistan, after 30 deaths in the past 24 hours [1, 2].
